altername_name: The Official PlayStation Magazine: Demo Disc 1
name: The Official PlayStation Magazine CD 1
overview: The first Europe Demo Disc that came with the Official Playstation 1 Magazine - This disc only released in the U.K. Playable Demos -3D Lemmings, Discworld and Novastorm Trailers -Assault Rigs, Destruction Derby, Krazy Ivan, Wipeout The demo disc also included a visual player for music discs.
